Manchester United vs Manchester City (Old Trafford) 

Team news

Manchester United

Manchester United have Chris Smalling back in contention after illness but Luke Shaw will not feature after a hamstring injury and fellow defender Jonny Evans is banned.

Striker Robin Van Persie will not be risked after ankle trouble, while midfielder Andreas Pereira is on Brazil Under 20 duty. 

